Package com.example.networkmeup.view.LoginTest

Class LoginViewStub

java.lang.Object
com.example.networkmeup.view.LoginTest.LoginViewStub
All Implemented Interfaces:
LoginView
public class LoginViewStub extends Object implements LoginView
This class acts as a stub implementation of the LoginView interface for testing purposes. It simulates a view and keeps track of employee and employer login actions.
